---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

SofaControl can use optional open-source components by Nefarius Software
Solutions. When bundled by the SofaControl installer, they are redistributed
unmodified under their own BSD-3-Clause licenses:

* ViGEmBus  - Virtual Gamepad Emulation Bus driver
              https://github.com/nefarius/ViGEmBus

* HidHide   - Optional controller hiding driver used by the pre-arm feature
              https://github.com/nefarius/HidHide

ViGEmClient, when linked into SofaControl.exe for virtual Xbox 360 support, is
also BSD-3-Clause, copyright Nefarius Software Solutions e.U.
